com.orientechnologies.orient.stresstest

Class OStressTesterCommandLineParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.orientechnologies.orient.stresstest.OStressTesterCommandLineParser

  • public class OStressTesterCommandLineParser
extends Object
    This is the parser of the command line arguments passed with the invocation of OStressTester. It contains a static method that - given the arguments - returns a OStressTester object.
    Author:
    Andrea Iacono
